Welcome to the 2023 Slovak Election Dashboard

This dashboard aggregates data from the Meta Ad Library to show how citizens are targeted during the 2023 Slovak parliamentary election.

If you want to know more about Who Targets Me and our work on ad transparency, visit us on whotargets.me!
